= Topic Assessment Overview

#info-box[
  *Assessment Details:*
  - *Total Questions:* ~20 (5 passages with 4 questions each)
  - *Time Limit:* 45 minutes (strictly timed)
  - *Average Pace:* 9 minutes per passage
  - *Topic:* Reading Comprehension
  - *Conducted In:* Lesson C
  - *Purpose:* Complete VR section, prepare for VR Section Assessments
]

#tip-box[
  *Note:* This is the final VR topic AND the final topic of the entire program! After this, students complete section assessments and mock simulations.
]

