= VR Section Completion Notes

#info-box[
  *Next Steps After Passing:*

  1. Schedule 3-4 VR Section Assessments (23 questions, 45 min each)
  2. Student must achieve cycle target score on 2+ assessments
  3. Upon successful completion, begin Full Mock Simulations (3-5 recommended)
  4. Ready for actual GMAT!
]

#highlight-box[
